altername_name: 인터랙티브 멀티 게임 체험판 디스크: 버전 33
name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc Version 33
overview: Interactive Multi Game Demo Disc v33 is a demo and video sampler disc, designed for retail store displays of the Nintendo GameCube. The sampler includes a simple menu and playable demos of Super Mario Strikers, Spartan: Total Warrior, Pokémon XD: Gale of Darkness, and Mario Party 7. The disc also features videos of: Prince of Persia: The Two Thrones, Fire Emblem: Path of Radiance, Need for Speed: Most Wanted, Spartan: Total Warrior, Tony Hawk's American Wasteland, Super Mario Strikers, X-Men Legends II: Rise of Apocalypse, Shadow the Hedgehog, Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire, Dance Dance Revolution: Mario Mix, The Sims 2, Mario Party 7, NBA Live 06, SSX on Tour, the Game Boy Micro, Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection, and an ESRB ratings video.
